headline: J.D. Power Recognizes Fifth Third as No. 1 for Banking Mobile App User Satisfaction Among Regional Banks
summary: CINCINNATI, May 29, 2025--J.D. Power today recognizes Fifth Third Bank (NASDAQ: FITB) as America’s best mobile banking app experience among regional banks as part of its 2025 U.S. Banking Mobile App Satisfaction StudySM. Study respondents also rate Fifth Third No. 1 for Visual Appeal.
